{"tid":2170803,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[C++新手] operator overloading 及const reference 一問","createTime":"2020-08-23T13:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T05:54:13.000Z","uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"33362d5f1371939029c5fd42f02139721d939772","tid":2170803,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T13:37:26.000Z","msg":"1. <code>int operator[](int i) const { };</code><br />\n2. <code>int&amp; operator[](int i) { };</code><br />\n<br />\n想問下1. 個const 加係後面既用處係咩，同我放前面const int 係咪一樣?<br />\n如果我overload呢個operator，佢點樣知我用1.定2.，定兩個都無所謂?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0756913704687ba6191876ef9df01c346716fd","tid":2170803,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T13:51:13.000Z","msg":"用1就無所謂"},{"pid":"4fee649a32005a3a1faf0515e8635bddcc75ce7b","tid":2170803,"uid":279606,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T13:59:18.000Z","msg":"1=只可以用同樣係const嘅method + immutable..."},{"pid":"4495b5d8a3bef122000ed8eac54bd3d510aeb24c","tid":2170803,"uid":71755,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T13:59:35.000Z","msg":"1. 係 const member function, 當個object係const嘅時候就會call呢個function<br />\n<br />\n對於呢個寫法<br />\n<code>const int operator[](int i) { };</code><br />\n<br />\nconst呢個keyword係冇用嘅，因為本身佢係return by value, 姐係佢係copy 個return value出去，所以const一個copied value係冇意義"},{"pid":"2e9b4eec9ed00d77b30de6b8920737d005c6f7b0","tid":2170803,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:54:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/34593263/c-overloading-operator\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstackoverflow.com%2Fquestions%2F34593263%2Fc-overloading-operator&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTHfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=eda5e12a\" target=\"_blank\">ht